flight of the navigator is a 1986 american science fiction adventure film directed by randal kleiser and written by mark h. baker , michael burton and matt macmanus . the film stars joey cramer as david freeman , a 12-year-old boy who is abducted by an alien spaceship and finds himself caught in a world that has changed around him . the film 's producers initially sent the project to walt disney pictures in 1984 , but the studio was unable to approve it and it was sent to producers sales organization , which made a deal with disney to distribute it in the united states . it was partially shot in fort lauderdale , florida and norway , it being a co-production with norwegian company viking film .